localized.title: 100 British English everyday expressions. (For sleeping, memorizing)
localized.description:
-. This is the second video.
 
I made a language learning (an app that can learn 10 languages ​​such as English). Through this app, as much as possible in a day
I plan to improve my English skills by creating content that can be learned in just a few hours.

I don't know how much time it will take, but let's try to do it.

Today, I made 100 everyday English that the British often use.
I plan to do it every day until I get used to English.


1. If you install the Android app called DeepShadowing, you can try more various functions.
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.touchizen.deepshadowing

   1) You can view both subtitles at the same time.
   2) You can use the shadowing technique.
   3) You can play the word game made with this video.
  
2. If you like me and want to improve your English, it would be nice to do it together.

3. If you would like to comment on other videos and the app, please give us your opinion and we will reflect it as much as possible.
